* Lakeflow\nPipelines Editor
** Development Features
*** Dry Run
****_ Validate pipeline code
****_ No data processing
****_ Catch syntax & dependency errors
*** Selective Execution
****_ Run a single file or table
****_ Faster iteration
*** Interactive DAG
****_ Visualize table dependencies
****_ Targeted table refreshes
****_ Execution metrics
*** Data Preview
****_ Sample streaming or mat. view data
****_ Verify transformation logic
** Note
***_ Pipeline definitions only
***_ Not regular notebook code
***_ pyspark.pipelines module required
